Actress Ruth Kadiri has welcomed a second child with her hubby, Ezerika. The movie star, who first embraced the joy of motherhood in 2019, welcomed her second child on Wednesday, July 20.   Davido joins JayJay Okocha at 2022 CAF awards     Tiwa Savage performs at 2022 CAF awards     Mr P replies to allegation of N7,000 fraud   In an Instagram post announcing the birth of her second daughter, the film maker said she prayed, waited and loved Emerald-Chizaram-Ezerika before her arrival. The newest mum shared photos holding the newborn while seated on the hospital bed alongside maternity shoots. She wrote: “Dear Emerald-Chizaram-Ezerika born 20th of July 2022. I want you to know that I prayed for you. Waited for you. Loved you before I met you. And you have made our lives a complete reminder that God answers prayers.”